[node name="goal" type="RichTextLabel" parent="canvas/ui/help_menu" unique_id=1635878386]
layout_mode = 0
offset_left = 34.0
offset_top = 62.0
offset_right = 339.0
offset_bottom = 413.0
theme_override_colors/default_color = Color(0, 0, 0, 1)
text = "The goal is to defeat all enemy dice to move on to the next round. Complete as many rounds as possible.

To kill an enemy damage must be dealt, 1 damage removes 1 face from an enemy die, once all faces are removed the enemy dies. Damage removes the current face, if the current face is blank then random faces are removed.

Left Click to select a die and to target other dice. Right Click to deselect a target and undo a selection."

[node name="legend" type="RichTextLabel" parent="canvas/ui/help_menu" unique_id=1931687404]
layout_mode = 0
offset_left = 349.0
offset_top = 64.0
offset_right = 868.0
offset_bottom = 384.0
theme_override_colors/default_color = Color(0, 0, 0, 1)
text = "Legend:
				- Deals 1, 2, and 3 damage
				- Blocks 1, 2, and 3 instances of damage (Enemy block must be selected first with damage)
			- Disables the effect of the target die.
			- Duplicates the selected face.
			- Rerolls the selected die, this action can be undone but rerolling will not produce a different result
			- Allows you to pick the face of one of your dice.
				- Heals 1, 2, and 3 HP."

